% zile, linux

# Start a buffer for temporary notes, which won't be saved
zile

# Open a file
zile <path_to_file>

# Save a file
Ctrl + X, Ctrl + S

# Quit
Ctrl + X, Ctrl + C

# Open a file at a specified line number
zile +<line_number> <path_to_file>

# Undo changes
Ctrl + X, U
